history.content: Try to enroll -- in a lab/dis section that has space.  If you are waitlisted, at that time e-mail me (sasson@berkeley.edu) and let me know your situation and I can help move you into the class.

Hi,

I am planning on registering for CS61A this Thursday during my Phase II appointment. I am an undeclared freshman with junior standing. On Telebears, however, the "Open Seating" category is full whereas the category "Students with a major of UNDECLARED or COGNITIVE SCIENCE or BIOENGINEERING and a class level of Freshman or Sophomore" is still open. I imagine that since on Telebears, I have junior standing, I will get waitlisted when I try to enroll.

How can I enroll in CS61A without getting waitlisted?
history.subject: Enrolling in CS61A as an undeclared freshman with junior standing
